{"tid":1516720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個朋友食左黑警老豆份家產","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:45:28.000Z","uid":75877,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ca74714c728f7a2cae9b4a27e802d33fe0a902","tid":1516720,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:06:37.000Z","msg":"有個朋友好撚高招<br />\n佢屋企兩層供滿既樓 自住老豆名 出租就老母名<br />\n前年仲買左層  落個仔名扮首置 但係黑警老豆做擔保<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排借D意話香港好亂乜乜就叫兩老加埋佢個名落個兩層樓<br />\n事成就同佢地反埋面<br />\n話諗緊賣唔賣左佢趕佢地訓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48d222e054b482d2439b6cfea2990e40ca3372d","tid":1516720,"uid":75877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"黑驚連屋都冇得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970806457cfbc47a26e7a0eb5ef25dc79541e831","tid":1516720,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831遊行<br />\n831死線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整咗兩張圖求大家幫手twitter spread出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eC9Jdp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eC9Jdp.png&h=c579fd37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbqfDMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbqfDMJ.png&h=fe574e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一定要通過人權法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e07ec5998f1ce5326ae12c81f703bf4d397ec55","tid":1516720,"uid":121255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"咁惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90eaa596326fb05bcc751c8940c3d9cb099ed74","tid":1516720,"uid":48679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n賣唔賣無所謂, 脫離親子關係再趕佢地出街"},{"pid":"d836818ace5fc0a05d438839d349bca852f9b746","tid":1516720,"uid":252523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"唔完美 可接受 需改善"},{"pid":"4420ff706020d9e4b3e211c7e3167ac4d994a6a3","tid":1516720,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"我地發起左<span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期日同五罷買</span>！FB已經有２萬人Like左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">下面有新ＰＯＳＴＥＲ，請廣傳     </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好需要大家都Like我地FB同簽名去嚮應呀！！</span></span><br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=364f0aef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n簽署ＬＩＮＫ 一定要簽 <a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=4c5c4e6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span></strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。<br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=6026b748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=fd07c12e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OkGHHu.jpg&h=ee06cc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0&amp;oe=5DD82060\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0%26oe%3D5DD82060&h=80325f8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"868e8f2b75c9ca538d5e6138033dd9809ab28c3e","tid":1516720,"uid":52090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪識你朋友？<br />\n宜家連個孫都唔比見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8674c1a26bdb35b957dfbe2f8decf61d30c0c5","tid":1516720,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}